Story:
     The CT's got information from an outside source that information on a terrorist cell they were tracking was left in an abandoned office. The T's got hold of the message and must prevent the CT's from gaining the information the only way they can. By blowing up the office and everything inside it.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- This medium sized map is great for every weapon, including snipers and shotguns.
The tight corners make sure of cover aand hiding places, yet people can still get you from behind.
